{"tid":502514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民今討論申司法覆核 消息指建制派輸官司即求釋法","createTime":"2017-12-18T03:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T03:32:42.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af969b9672072580920690cf76a9dc608474975c","tid":502514,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171218/large/1513566949_0860.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171218%2Flarge%2F1513566949_0860.jpg&h=02903fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會上周通過建制派提出的《議事規則》修訂，其中有關全體委員大會法定人數由35人減至20人，被指違反《基本法》，立會議員朱凱廸指泛民今日將討論是否須由議員申請司法覆核，及是否由全體泛民負責。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸指有消息稱建制派不怕官司，指就算輸亦可以申請人大釋法，他表示即使如此亦需要申請司法覆核，尋求一個原審過程。朱又指，曾就議事規則與主席梁君彥會面，指梁亦不確定有關修訂有否違反《基本法》，指只有法官才能裁定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171218/57595715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171218%2F57595715&d=bGNBR22iDGm65AEqoHDsIP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=9c1eba81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171218%2F57595715&h=3516e8c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171218/57595715</a>"},{"pid":"d2fd2e0e28a1c96d5a34bb4825b3c559efc0bb2d","tid":502514,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171218/s00001/093ed0e9a30fb574dda9feadf2d81391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171218%2Fs00001%2F093ed0e9a30fb574dda9feadf2d81391.jpg&h=a077b99e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}